  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
     
        <div xml:id="Aink343">
            <lg type="edition">
            <l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
            <l>tiṇinilaik kōṅkam payanta</l>
            <l>vaṇimiku koḻumukai yuṭaiyum poḻutē</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
             <l>Oh, indeed he isn’t coming! [But] the season has come,</l>  
             <l>when thick buds of great beauty,  </l>
             <l>produced by the myrobalan that has firmness, blossom.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
